External use only;
Do not use if pregnant or breastfeeding;
Always use sunscreen the morning after the peelings in order to minimize the risk of sun sensitivity;
A slight stinging may occur and is normal in the first applications;
Avoid mucosas, open wounds, previous inflammation and the eyes and lips areas.

